body:

Ce site est fait avec (Lektor)[https://getlektor.com] et chacun peut participer à sa construction sur https://github.com/EduCodeBe/educode.be

Il a vocation à être multilingue et nécessite pour cela votre aide pour les tradcutions, relectures, commentaires, illustrations ...

---
about:

This site is made with the [free software] (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Free_software) multiplatform and multilingual [Lektor] (https://getlektor.com). 

It is developed jointly on [github] (https://github.com/EduCodeBe/educode.be) and anyone who wants to help, even modestly, contribute to corrections, modifications, translations ... can do it easily. 

For example, for a suggestion or a comment, please fill out the [form] (https://github.com/EduCodeBe/educode.be/issues/new)
